    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，\"Section\"部分已经加上了。那\"Another\" section呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Section",
        "A task",
        "Another task"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "\"Another\"下面也有两个任务。第一个\"Task in Another\"从1月12日开始，持续12天；第二个\"another task\"持续时间24天——这个的起始时间我没特别指定，让它紧接前一个任务就行。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Task in Another",
        "2014-01-12",
        "12d",
        "another task",
        "24d"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：第二个任务\"another task\"24天，是接在\"Task in Another\"之后对吧？不需要显式写after？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "another task",
        "Task in Another",
        "24d"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就按默认的紧接方式处理，不写after了。图的整体标题就叫\"A Gantt Diagram\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "another task"
